description: In Part 2 of the Masqulin Impulse Buy series, Markus Kage makes a detour to the underbelly of the store where he discovers a very naked and ready Alex Mecum blindfolded and ass up. Markus has a decision to make. He can turn around and pretend he never saw this or he can allow himself to venture into unchartered territories.
title: IMPULSE BUY - PART 2: Markus Kage and Alex Mecum RAW
